---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
   <main class="m-auto max-w-[100ch]">
      <h1 class="text-4xl pb-3 pt-7" >Our Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="pb-10">
         Urban Forest Ecosystem Institute is committed to protecting your privacy. This
         privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you
         use SelecTree, our website that provides information about trees and their
         characteristics.
      </p>

      <Section 
         title="What data do we collect?"
         body={"We collect personal identification information such as your name, email address and phone number. We also collect data about the trees you search for, the pages you visit, and your IP address."}
      />

      <Section 
         title="How do we collect your data?"
         body="We collect your data when you visit our website, search for trees, make lists / saved searches, create an account, or contact us for support. We also collect data using cookies and similar technologies."
      />

      <Section 
         title="How will we use your data?"
         body=" We will use your data to provide you with information about trees and their characteristics. We may also use your data to improve our website and services, as well as to send you marketing communications about our products and services."
      />

      <Section 
         title="How do we store your data?"
         body="We store your data in secure databases and servers located in the United States. We use appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, disclosure, or destruction."
      />

      <Section 
         title="What are your data protection rights?"
         body="You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You can also object to the processing of your personal data, request a restriction on its processing, or request its transfer to another party. To exercise your rights, please contact us using the information provided below."
      />

      <Section 
         title="What are cookies?"
         body="Cookies are small files that contain information about your website preferences and activity. We use cookies to improve your browsing experience, personalize content, and analyze website traffic."
      />

      <Section 
         title="How do we use cookies?"
         body="We use cookies to remember your preferences, provide you with personalized content, and analyze how you use our website. We also use cookies to serve you with targeted advertising based on your browsing activity."
      />

      <Section 
         title="What types of cookies do we use?"
         body="We use functional cookies that enable basic website functions and cannot be switched off. We also use analytics cookies to track website usage and performance, as well as advertising cookies to serve you with targeted ads."
      />

      <Section 
         title="How to manage cookies?"
         body="You can disable cookies in your browser settings or by using an ad blocker. However, some parts of our website may not function properly without cookies."
      />

      <Section 
         title="Privacy policies of other websites"
         body=" Our website may contain links to other websites that have their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of other websites and encourage you to read their privacy statements."
      />

      <Section 
         title="Changes to our privacy policy"
         body="We may update our privacy policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on our website."
      />
      <Section 
         title="How to contact us"
         body="If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at support@selectree.com."
      />
      <Section 
         title="How to contact the appropriate authorities"
         body="If you believe that we have not addressed your privacy concerns satisfactorily, you may contact your local data protection authority."
      />

   </main>
</Layout>
